            "value": "<h1>Severity model</h1><p>SEV-1 incidents require commander assignment within 5 minutes.</p><h2>Communication</h2><p>Post updates every 15 minutes in the incident channel.</p><h2>Escalation matrix</h2><ol><li>Notify the commander</li><li>Page the owning team</li></ol>"
